dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: Fire Stations are a subset of buildings derived from the Public Service Buildings and Facilities (PSBF) data set.  This data is refreshed periodically, as the master data set is updated (view code). Point locations are registered to the Snohomish PUD parcels, and the Street centerline coverage. Contains name, address, and other information.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
